Brtue force-TC=O(N)
A Simple Approach is to traverse the given array one by one and compare every element with given element ‘x’. If matches, then return index.

TC=O(N),SC=O(1)
The above solution can be Optimized using the fact that difference between all adjacent elements is 1.

int search(int arr[], int n, int x)
{
    // Traverse the given array starting from
    // leftmost element
    int i = 0;
    while (i<n)
    {
        if (arr[i] == x)
            {return i;}
            
        i = i + abs(arr[i]-x);
    }
    return -1;
}
